headline: CoStar Group Names Grant Montgomery as National Director of Multifamily Analytics
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., July 23, 2025--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, analytics, and 3D digital twin technology in the property markets, announced today the appointment of Grant Montgomery as National Director of Multifamily Analytics. The hire will augment the company’s already powerful analytics across the U.S. multifamily sector, adding value for CoStar Group clients and the commercial real estate industry as a whole.
